data.description: You'll love the simple beauty of this home! The great room includes an open concept living, dining, and kitchen with a large center island perfect for entertaining! The kitchen includes a Thor cooktop and double Frigidaire ovens. The fireplace makes for a beautiful focal point that blends perfectly with the attached rooms. The master and one other bedroom are downstairs with their own en suite bathrooms. The master bathroom includes a large soaking tub and walk in shower. Upstairs you'll find a bonus room that is perfect for relaxing or for the kids to play in. There are two more bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom between the two.
